OL,5,G1030 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FTensions are already bubbling away
OL,7,     Fbetween the B&Bers before they've
OL,8,     Feven arrived at Ying and Jean's
OL,9,     FCastle Inn, in Powys. But the
OL,10,     Fhosts have the answer to restore
OL,11,     Fharmony: pies.
OL,12,G1100 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FIt's payment day. Nowhere else
OL,14,     Fwill you find such consternation
OL,15,     Fabout whether a double bed is
OL,16,     Freally a double bed if it's two
OL,17,     Fsingle beds pushed together. But
OL,18,     Fwho's won?
